WEBVTT

00:11.345 --> 00:13.514
<i>I felt hungrier than ever.</i>

00:14.598 --> 00:16.850
<i>But it wasn't just my stomach
that felt empty.</i>

00:17.768 --> 00:21.230
<i>Nonnie had dumped me,
my mom ran off to who knows where,</i>

00:21.563 --> 00:25.108
<i>and Bob Armstrong hated me
for outing him and Bob Barnard.</i>

00:26.610 --> 00:27.986
<i>And who could blame him?</i>

00:28.278 --> 00:29.571
<i>I hated me too.</i>

00:30.405 --> 00:32.448
<i>I spent the last week hiding out,</i>

00:32.533 --> 00:35.911
<i>stuffing my face,
and already none of my pants fit.</i>

00:37.621 --> 00:41.124
<i>I knew food wasn't gonna fix my problems,
but what else could I do?</i>

00:47.673 --> 00:49.758
<i>And then I got my answer.</i>

00:50.842 --> 00:53.845
<i>Drew Barrymore was coming to Atlanta?</i>

00:54.137 --> 00:56.306
<i>It was divine intervention,</i>

00:56.807 --> 00:58.809
<i>like a sign from God herself.</i>

01:00.060 --> 01:03.480
<i>Drew wouldn't give up like a loser
and eat her way into oblivion.</i>

01:04.063 --> 01:06.400
<i>So, what would Drew Barrymore do?</i>

